OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fdispersing this morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FWarm inland, but cooler along the east
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry and clear with
OL,14,Fsome patchy fog and low cloud. Patchy
OL,15,Ffrost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FDry with some sunshine in the
OL,18,Fmorning. Clouding over from the
OL,19,Fsouthwest in the afternoon with some
OL,20,Fshowery rain extending northeast
OL,21,Flater. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
