OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCooler
OL,6,Fand cloudy over the weekend with a
OL,7,Fchance of showers, these most
OL,8,Fwidespread on Saturday. Showery rain
OL,9,Fspreading southeast for a time on
OL,10,FMonday then dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
